 [schema type=&quot;review&quot; name=&quot;Social Media in Emergencies&quot; description=&quot;With the fast ..." /><meta property="og:description" content="Social Media in Emergency Situations         (Image from http://www.prafulla.net/interesting-contents/social-networks/social-media-and-emergency-response-infographic/).      [schema type=&quot;review&quot; name=&quot;Social Media in Emergencies&quot; description=&quot;With the fast ..." /> <style type="text/css" id="custom-background-css">body.custom-background{background-image:url('http://www.robertattfield.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/bg-tile.png');background-repeat:repeat;background-position:top left;background-attachment:fixed}</style><style type="text/css" id="syntaxhighlighteranchor"></style><link rel="stylesheet" id="custom-css-css" type="text/css" href="http://www.robertattfield.com/blog/?custom-css=1&#038;csblog=1&#038;cscache=6&#038;csrev=229" /><script type="text/javascript">var _gaq=_gaq||[];_gaq.push(['_setAccount','UA-37595549-1']);_gaq.push(['_trackPageview']);(function(){var ga=document.createElement('script');ga.type='text/javascript';ga.async=true;ga.src=('https:'==document.location.protocol?'https://ssl':'http://www')+'.google-analytics.com/ga.js';var s=document.getElementsByTagName('script')[0];s.parentNode.insertBefore(ga,s);})();</script></head><body id="#top" class="single single-post postid-356 single-format-standard custom-background"><div id="container"> <header class="header" role="banner"><div id="inner-header" class="wrap clearfix"><p id="logo" class="h1" style="margin-top: 100px;"><a href="http://www.robertattfield.com/blog" rel="nofollow">The Blog of Rob Attfield</a></p> I post about S.E.O, Social Media, Web Development, Wordpress, and the W.W.W. <nav role="navigation"><ul id="menu-main-menu" class="nav top-nav clearfix"><li id="menu-item-29" class="menu-item menu-item-type-post_type menu-item-object-page menu-item-29"><a href="http://www.robertattfield.com/blog/">Home</a><